content.rendered:
Directed by Japinder Kaur Baweja.

Written by Manu Rishi Chadha.

Cast Divyendu Sharma(Dhruv). Jackie Shroff(Minocha). Prachi Mishra(Sakshi). Ira Dubey(Nimmy). Pradhuman Singh(Happy) . Natalia Kapchuk(Singer). Vijay Meenu(Mrs. Minocha). Elly Meyers(Dancer). Deepaq Sharma(Mohanlal)

Language Hindi.

Producers Vicky Bhatia. Sanjay Inamdar. Kailash Khatri K.K.. Kamlesh Puri. Tarnpreet Singh.
